data.description: Welcome to your perfect retirement haven with this great 2 bedroom, 2 bath, office niche home located in the desirable 55+ community of SunRiver.  This home is loaded w/ upgrades from new 6 person hot tub, golfcart, security doors & cameras, water softener, r/o system, granite counters, new sink & touchless faucet, updated electrical switches/plugs as well as a walk-in tub/shower to name a few! Enjoy the outdoors w/ a spacious, gated front courtyard & private back yard which is beautifully landscaped w/ a covered patio & comes w/ a natural gas BBQ. The heated/cooled 2.5 car garage is perfect for all your toys & hobby's.  In addition to your haven you have access to the 35,000 sq ft community center with endless amenities & activities. This home is a must see!!
